    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="../index.html" class="nav-logo">
                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                Career Explorer
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="../index.html" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="../index.html#features" class="nav-link">Features</a></li>
                <li><a href="../index.html#demo" class="nav-link">Demo</a></li>
                <li><a href="../index.html#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-fashion">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i> Fashion Design
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Unleash your creativity and design the future of fashion. Explore the glamorous world of fashion design, from concept to runway.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="section-content">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <div class="content-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Introduction to Fashion Design</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Fashion Design is a creative field that combines art, technology, and business to create clothing, accessories, and lifestyle products. It involves conceptualizing designs, selecting fabrics, creating patterns, and overseeing the production process. Fashion designers shape trends, express cultural movements, and meet consumer needs while balancing creativity with commercial viability.</p>
                <br>
                <p>This field requires a blend of artistic vision, technical skills, and business acumen. Fashion designers work in various sectors including haute couture, ready-to-wear, accessories, footwear, and sustainable fashion.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Branches/Specializations -->
            <div class="content-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="card-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-sitemap"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Branches & Specializations</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="specialization-grid">
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-crown" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Haute Couture</h4>
                        <p>High-end custom fashion for elite clientele</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-tshirt" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Ready-to-Wear</h4>
                        <p>Mass market clothing production</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Accessories Design</h4>
                        <p>Bags, jewelry, belts, and fashion accessories</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Sustainable Fashion</h4>
                        <p>Eco-friendly and ethical fashion solutions</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-running" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Footwear Design</h4>
                        <p>Shoes, sneakers, and footwear innovation</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="spec-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-baby" style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ff6b9d;"></i>
                        <h4>Children's Wear</h4>
                        <p>Specialized fashion for kids and infants</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Eligibility & Entrance Exams -->
